text: Pál Pajzs (27 April 1886 - 1966) was a Hungarian fencer. He competed in the individual sabre and foil events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1886 births Category:1966 deaths Category:Sportspeople from Székesfehérvár Category:Hungarian male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Hungary Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
